text: Dibër may refer to: *Dibër valley, known today as "Two Dibers", a tribal- highland region of north Albania with the administrative and commercial center in Debar that was split between Albania and Yugoslavia (today North Macedonia) *Dibër County, a county in Albania *Dibër District, a district in Dibër County, Albania *Dibër (municipality), Dibër District, Dibër County, Albania *Debar, a town in Debar Municipality, North Macedonia
title: Dibër
